title: 记忆链接错误码
summary: Multimodal Awareness Kit Msdp 模块的 记忆链接错误码，提供相关接口和功能说明。

sections.title: 32100001 文件创建失败
sections.summary:
**错误信息**  
Internal handling failed. File creation failed.  

**错误描述**  
当调用记忆链接模块接口时，若服务异常，会报此错误码。

sections.title: 32100002 编码程序执行失败
sections.summary:
**错误信息**  
Encoding failed. Possible causes: 1. Image processing error; 2. Channel coding error. 

*

sections.title: 32100003 解码程序执行失败
sections.summary:
**错误码信息**  
Decoding failed. Possible causes: 1. Image not encoded; 2. Image destroyed. 

**错误描述**
